Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto

Class DataTypeName

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto.DataTypeName
Direct Known Subclasses:
DaTypeName, DoTypeName
public class DataTypeName extends Object
A representation of the model object Data Type Name.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Refers to middle name part of a structured data name

    Example of instantiated subdata 

              
              <DOI name=”X”>
                  <SDI name=”X”>
                      <SDI name=”X”>
                          <DAI name=”X” />
                      </SDI>
                  </SDI>
              </DOI>
